# 3.1.1.research.external.q6.rate-limit-scope

## question

is rate limit purely per-token, or does IP/device factor in?

## options

- per-token only (rotation will work)
- per-IP (rotation won't help from same machine)
- per-device/fingerprint
- combination

## why it matters

if rate limit is per-IP, token rotation won't help. design premise fails.

## research approach

check anthropic rate limit docs, empirical test with multiple tokens from same IP.

## note

marked as [wisher] in vision — may require empirical validation.

## .status

awaited
